// WaveTerm BYOK AI Modes — paste content into Wave Config → Wave AI Modes
// Set API keys via: wsh secret set GROQ_API_KEY=<value>
//                   wsh secret set MISTRAL_API_KEY=<value>
// The "ai:apitokensecretname" references the wsh secret name (not the value directly)
// Reference: https://docs.waveterm.dev/reference/ai-modes
